Interface OperatingSystem

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CommunicationModuleOwner
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ChargingStationOperatingSystem, ElectricVehicleOperatingSystem, RoadSideUnitOperatingSystem, ServerOperatingSystem, TrafficLightOperatingSystem, TrafficManagementCenterOperatingSystem, VehicleOperatingSystem
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractSimulationUnit, ChargingStationUnit, ElectricVehicleUnit, RoadSideUnit, ServerUnit, TrafficLightGroupUnit, TrafficManagementCenterUnit, VehicleUnit
    public interface OperatingSystem
extends CommunicationModuleOwner
    This interface describes all necessary functionality for units to be simulated.

        default long getSimulationTimeMs()
        Returns the time difference in milliseconds since a well-defined start time - here milliseconds since the simulation start time. 1.1.1970 00:00:00.000 Needs to be aligned with SAE J2735 DF_DDateTime, DF_DTime, DE_DSecond. Unit: [ms].
        Returns:
